     1‚Üí# humanize
    12‚ÜíThis modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13‚Üínumber into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14‚Üísize or throughput. It is localized to:
    15‚Üí
    16‚Üí- Arabic
    17‚Üí- Basque
    18‚Üí- Bengali
    19‚Üí- Brazilian Portuguese
    20‚Üí- Catalan
    21‚Üí- Danish
    22‚Üí- Dutch
    23‚Üí- Esperanto
    24‚Üí- European Portuguese
    25‚Üí- Finnish
    26‚Üí- French
    27‚Üí- German
    28‚Üí- Greek
    29‚Üí- Hebrew
    30‚Üí- Indonesian
    31‚Üí- Italian
    32‚Üí- Japanese
    33‚Üí- Klingon
    34‚Üí- Korean
    35‚Üí- Norwegian
    36‚Üí- Persian
    37‚Üí- Polish
    38‚Üí- Russian
    39‚Üí- Simplified Chinese
    40‚Üí- Slovak
    41‚Üí- Slovenian
    42‚Üí- Spanish
    43‚Üí- Swedish
    44‚Üí- Turkish
    45‚Üí- Ukrainian
    46‚Üí- Uzbek
    47‚Üí- Vietnamese
    48‚Üí
